[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "尤弥尔消失了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "并不全是因为里芙——也许它注意到了远处正在启动的电磁炮“萨迦”，也许是埃达已经达到了它的目的，总之，尤弥尔的身体逐渐消失了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "伴随着那可怕的压迫感烟消云散，一道道光穿过楼间狭隙，随后是雨滴。很快，雨点连成柱般，冲刷着我脸上的血痕。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这场仿佛不会停下的雪，也在不知不觉间融化了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "耳边逐渐传来踩踏水洼的声音，透过雨幕，我看到一个摇晃的身影缓缓朝我走来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-1",
        "Flag": "b-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "b-1-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "里芙？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "b-1-2",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "星期三？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "闪电照亮了来者的脸庞。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "奥丁……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "雨水打湿了她的头发，顺着脸颊从下巴滴落。蓝色的眼瞳中，看不到熟悉的眼神。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "幽蓝色雷电在她的手中汇聚，形成长枪，枪尖几乎直顶着我的心脏。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-2",
        "Flag": "b-2",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "b-2-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "躲开雷枪",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "b-2-1-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "身体先一步做出行动，我猛地侧身避开雷枪，继而右腿发力，快速拉近与里芙的距离，将其紧紧抱住。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "b-2-1-2",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但这片刻间已经给了里芙反应的机会，她迅速抓住了我握着注射弹的右手。只一瞬间，我便感觉自己失去了对右手的控制，注射弹也应声掉落。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "b-2-2",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "直面雷枪",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "b-2-2-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没有丝毫犹豫，我咬着牙冲向里芙，任凭雷枪穿过我的身体。麻痹感立刻传遍全身，但我仍凭着最后的力气蹬向地面——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "b-2-2-2",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "如此不计代价的动作让里芙都不禁愣住，转瞬之间，她便被我推到墙边。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "b-2-2-3",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "然而，在我反应过来时才发现，在短暂失去身体控制权的时候，我本来握在手中的注射弹已经不知道落在了哪里，此时我的手中空空如也。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "发觉我并没有进一步的动作后，怀中的里芙愈发躁动。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……哈，我刚回到公司，当上分析员后的第一个任务，你也是这样，对我……毫不留情。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "电流顺着我们紧贴的皮肤传遍我的全身，我甚至感觉自己闻到了毛发焦糊的味道。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那次还只是神格侵蚀，这次……可麻烦多了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "头像是要炸开一样，眩晕感直冲脑门，如两双大手撕裂着我的意识。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不过放心好了，我还是……不会松手的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "去他*的奥丁，我不会让你变成没有人性的怪物的……把我的里芙，还回来！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……滚开。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在我几乎力尽时，里芙忽然没头没脑地骂了一句，而我很快意识到，这并非说给我听。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "伴随着话语，她那不属于人类的神瞳快速消失，取而代之的是一双透露着难以掩饰的疲惫的眼睛。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "然后，没有任何征兆的，雷电消散，面前的少女就这样倒在了我的怀中。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她的呼吸和身体一样轻，有那么一瞬间，我想到了最坏的可能性。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "还好，只是耗尽力气了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "远处，更多的脚步声和呼喊声逐渐清晰。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "是时候带她回家了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一天后。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在公司医疗室的病床上醒来时，我一眼便看到在门外踱步的里芙。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "大概是医生三令五申要让我静养，她才一直在外面等着吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "床头柜上摆放着我的终端，我草草看了一眼。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "置顶的一条是陶的消息，理所当然的，她对我和里芙私自闯入深水区的行为颇有微词，让我康复后和她当面聊聊。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而后的十几条则来自我的队员们——不必多说，病房中摆满的慰问品也是来自于她们。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我摇了摇头，草草披上放在一旁的外衣，推开了门。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "里芙，我……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在我开口的瞬间，面前的少女紧紧抱住了我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那个在旁人眼中，冷得像冰山一样的女孩，此时正将她大半个身子的体温和重量都倾注在我身上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就好像，我们分开了许多年。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "太好了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她小声地呢喃了一句，我几乎是通过肩骨上传来的震动才确定她发出了声音。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哈……我这不是好端端地在这儿嘛……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "又是一声呢喃。我开始担心她是不是已经哭得梨花带雨，却突然被往前推了半步。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "少女的眼中果然带着泪花，眼神却无比地坚决。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我当时，还没来得及回应你……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我不想再失去你了，绝对绝对不会……！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我没听到她说出后半句话。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "因为说到一半时，她就踮起脚，捧住了我的脸——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "又一次将她的温度传递过来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……被女孩子主动，这好像是第一次？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我的脑中如烟花般蹦出无数个想法，但最终，这些细碎的念头都合而为一。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "<orange>我也不想再失去她。</>",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不过，这句话还是留到结束以后，再慢慢告诉她吧。",
        "disable": 0
    }
]